# Shell directory contract

**Replaces:** `workbench-directory.mdc`, `app-shell-directory.mdc`
**Doctrine:** ADR-0001 (Spatial OS), ADR-0005 (shell unification). If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md`.

---

## New shell: `components2/app-shell/` (canonical from now on)

`components2/app-shell/` is the **replacement shell** for new route wiring. Import via `#app-shell`.

**Org ERP modules** mount under `/o/{orgSlug}/apps/{module}` (ADR-0029). One `AppShell` at `o/[orgSlug]/layout.tsx` only — no `apps/layout.tsx` utility bar. `AppSubLayout` only on modules with a secondary rail (HRM, admin).

Shell-level **React providers** live in **`components2/providers/`** (sibling of `app-shell/`, not nested under it). Shell-level **Zustand stores** live in **`components2/stores/`** (same). The `#app-shell` barrel still re-exports `useAppShellStore` for a single public door.

### Public exports

| Symbol                                           | File                                                         | Usage                                                 |
| ------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| `AppShell`                                       | `appshell.tsx`                                               | Org root layout.tsx (RSC entry)                       |
| `AppShellClient`                                 | `appshell.client.tsx`                                        | Client chrome — mounts AppShellProviders, utility bar |
| `AppSubLayout`                                   | `surface/appshell-sub-layout.tsx`                            | Nested layout.tsx (admin, HRM) — in-flow aside        |
| `AppSubLayoutClient`                             | `surface/appshell-sub-layout.client.tsx`                     | Client chrome — in-flow aside, local collapse state   |
| `AppShellPrimaryLeftRail`                        | `left-rail-bar/appshell-primary-left-rail.client.tsx`        | Primary left rail (search, lanes, nav sections)       |
| `AppShellSubNav` / `AppShellSubNavFloatingPanel` | `surface/appshell-sub-layout-left-rail.client.tsx`           | AppSubLayout tree rail + floating overlay             |
| `AppShellPrimaryLeftRailRaw`                     | `left-rail-bar/appshell-primary-left-rail-raw.client.tsx`    | Primary sidebar nav rows (`SidebarMenuButton`)        |
| `AppShellContextMenu`                            | `left-rail-bar/appshell-context-menu.client.tsx`             | Right-click add-to-memory wrapper                     |
| `AppShellPrimaryLeftRailFooter`                  | `left-rail-bar/appshell-primary-left-rail-footer.client.tsx` | Rail mode control (expanded / hover / collapsed)      |
| `AppShellSurface`                                | `surface/appshell-sub-layout-surface.tsx`                    | Page content region (breadcrumbs + body)              |
| `AppShellUtilityBar`                             | `top-utils-bar/appshell-utility-bar.tsx`                     | L1 top bar (slots only, no business logic)            |
