### `components2/providers/` — individual React context providers

| Symbol                    | File                                                   | Purpose                                                        |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `AppShellTooltipProvider` | `components2/providers/tooltip-provider.client.tsx`    | shadcn Tooltip delay, shell-scoped                             |
| `AppShellSidebarProvider` | `components2/providers/sidebar-provider.client.tsx`    | shadcn SidebarProvider with shell CSS vars + wraps full column |
| `AppShellProviders`       | `components2/providers/app-shell-providers.client.tsx` | Composes all providers — mount once in `AppShellClient`        |

**Key invariant:** `AppShellSidebarProvider` wraps the **entire shell column** including the utility bar header. This is intentional — utility-bar components can call `useSidebar()` to control rail collapse without a separate context.

Adding a new provider: create `components2/providers/<concept>-provider.client.tsx`, then compose it inside `app-shell-providers.client.tsx`. One file to change, one place to reason about.

### `components2/stores/` — Zustand state (cross-cutting, context-free)

| Symbol             | File                                    | State owned                        |
| ------------------ | --------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `useAppShellStore` | `components2/stores/app-shell.store.ts` | `commandOpen`, `notificationCount` |

Zustand stores need no `<Provider>` — import `useAppShellStore` from `#app-shell/client` (not `#app-shell`; the server barrel is `server-only`).

Adding new shell state: extend `AppShellStore` in `app-shell.store.ts`. If the store grows beyond ~6 actions, split into a new file under `components2/stores/`.

**Import aliases:** `#app-shell` → `./components2/app-shell/index.ts` (server-only barrel) · `#app-shell/client` → `./components2/app-shell/client.ts`.
**Import alias:** `#components2/*` → `./components2/*` (direct access to components2 primitives). **`#components2`** (barrel) exports only `GovernedComponentRenderer` + registry — not shell or UI. Metadata kernel: `components2/metadata/` (ADR-0021). Playground shell preview: `components2/playground/app-shell-preview/`.

