## Route layout facade (`AppShell` / `AppSubLayout`)

- **Production org/console layouts** import **`AppShell`** from **`#app-shell`** (`components2/app-shell/appshell.tsx`) with slot props: `utilityBar`, `rail`, `command`, `overlay`, `envelope`.
- **Client chrome** (command palette, utility controls, rail footer): **`#app-shell/client`** only — never import `#app-shell` from Client Components (`server-only` barrel).
- **Server composers:** `buildAppShellOrgUtilityBarSlots` / `buildAppShellBootstrapUtilityBarSlots` in `components2/app-shell/compose/`.
- **No** `components2/app-shell/workbench/` — deleted; no `WorkbenchShell` alias on the public barrel.

